gt;14）仆街代理令市民買樓卻步&lt;br/&gt;15）資訊大爆發，市民知道樓市充滿陷阱&lt;br/&gt;16）天價大廈維修&lt;br/&gt;17）管理費不斷加&lt;br/&gt;18）租金回報不理想，其實而家只係去到2019嗰價，扣除雜費，買收息股仲好&lt;br/&gt;19）投資產品越來越多，投資不動產，笑&lt;br/&gt;20）政策市，房住不炒&lt;br/&gt;21）新香港人，攞福利或以香港做踏腳石&lt;br/&gt;22）老美関稅戰&lt;br/&gt;23）大到不能倒的地產商都叫救命&lt;br/&gt;24）樓市炒家被call loan , 清盤、破產&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31968463&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=10915923016860c10ab48037_28395876"/><published>2025-06-28T15:07:52+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>45cf925e2e301feceaa0a431451078d6</id><title>睇你敢買樓 ？</title><updated>2025-06-28T16:02:25+08:00</updated><author><name>smart004</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-06-28T16:02:25+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573025798"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573025798"&gt;租客 変 租霸&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stheadline.com%2Finvestment%2F3459143%2F%25E5%25BD%25A2%25E5%258B%25A2%25E9%25BA%25BB%25E9%25BA%25BB%25E4%25B8%2594%25E5%258D%2587%25E4%25B8%2594%25E6%25B2%25BD%25E6%259B%25BE%25E6%2599%25BA%25E8%258F%25AF&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=6b2f49dacbd4076221abb6e5e8dbbba0&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank"&gt;https://www.stheadline.com/investment/3459143/形勢麻麻且升且沽曾智華&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31968504&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=10915923016860c10ab48037_28395876"/><published>2025-06-28T16:02:25+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>c9f78778acd0dd6ab21232d1b5d0e9e1</id><title>如果短期內長和系要撤出香港，將手頭